      <title>中国向企业提供数十年前的税单，暗示融资困难</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/china-hands-firms-decades-old-tax-bills-hinting-at-funding-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国地方政府已要求多家企业缴纳自上世纪 90 年代以来的税款，凸显出在经济复苏不平衡和房地产市场持续低迷的情况下，这些企业需要资金支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/china-hands-firms-decades-old-tax-bills-hinting-at-funding-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 03:24:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行称中国需要“新刺激”来支持经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-17/china-needs-new-stimulus-to-support-growth-bofa-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行的乔海伦表示，中国的总需求状况“仍然相对疲软”，需要“新的刺激措施”来支撑增长势头。周一公布的经济数据显示，中国 5 月份工业扩张放缓，2024 年前五个月房地产开发投资同比下降 10.1%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-17/china-needs-new-stimulus-to-support-growth-bofa-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 03:08:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国水电发展推动铝产量创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/china-s-hydropower-surge-raises-aluminum-production-to-a-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着冶炼厂恢复闲置产能，中国铝产量上个月创下历史新高，这可能导致铝市场在 5 月份触及两年高点后进一步下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/china-s-hydropower-surge-raises-aluminum-production-to-a-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 03:00:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国经济数据好坏参半，工业金属价格进一步下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/industrial-metals-deepen-retreat-after-mixed-china-economic-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国经济数据凸显持续疲软表现——尤其是金属密集型的房地产行业——之后，铁矿石价格下跌逾2%，铜价延续近期跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/industrial-metals-deepen-retreat-after-mixed-china-economic-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 02:59:30 GMT</pubDate>
